{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2597ab70e7","title":"中共中央关于制止西藏武斗的五项指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6d73d8d7a7","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"2597ab70e7"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"94b82e4994","name":"中共中央决定、指示等","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"c0cd6cf1d4","name":"边境地区和少数民族","type":"主题"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"300de6ee9e","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于制止西藏武斗的五项指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"f61ec3b6ad","type":"paragraph","text":"一、会议听取两派情况的全面汇报以后，中央认为：造总、大联指均定为群众组织，以便实现大批判、大联合。两派的性质暂不下文字的东西。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"cfb70dba1b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、拉萨各派组织，必须马上停止武斗，不准调农牧民进城，立即恢复交通运输，抓革命促生产、促战备、促工作，认真学习中央文件、江青等同志讲话和报纸的社论，这些是对各革命群众组织的考验。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"2a7baeea15","type":"paragraph","text":"三、要防止挑拨离间，调拨民族关系。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"4ac607f518","type":"paragraph","text":"四、报纸是传达毛主席和党中央声音的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"692f084465","type":"paragraph","text":"五、如何做得好，这是对各革命群众组织的考验，还有一点要向造总同志传达的，“专打”不能定为群众组织、中央认为它是有错误的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"0e4f581ce4","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"},{"id":"607c6e7bf8","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年九月十八日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7"}],"page":{"id":"2f5c50c52e","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2597ab70e7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}